{"tid":558053,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人長期便秘，但一離開香港就無事？","createTime":"2018-02-12T02:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T16:22:08.000Z","uid":19657,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"789832e76fa334c2378de31fe9697ae08ba7b0b5","tid":558053,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"係香港生活咗22年，日日都便秘<br />\n長期食菜、水果，一星期有兩三日會做下運動<br />\n火龍果、鹽水、西梅汁乜都試過<br />\n<br />\n直到有一次去日本旅行，去六日，六日個肚都準時7點幾叫我起身，10分鐘就痾乾淨個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後行街個人好似識飛咁，做咗廿年人都未試過咁輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n點知一返香港就打回原形，諗住可能日本食咗啲咩先會咁<br />\n<br />\n過咗半年又去多次，嗰四日又係日日輕鬆愉快，我覺得可能日本啲飲食問題掛<br />\n<br />\n直到上年有啲事返咗大陸，鄉下嗰邊，住咗一個月，頂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成個月都係7點起身痾屎，琴日食咗啲乜今日就痾返出嚟，我日日都觀察住啲屎，正常顏色，一條條，唔乾唔爛，日日都好似見到彩虹咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係返到香港第一日又便秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a7dc8833f555f4107340c393e059e3e386bd7a","tid":558053,"uid":65818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"水質？"},{"pid":"fdb24fb8fc0bb98b6ca9b0edd116125548b539d3","tid":558053,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"係咪壓力問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28608bc91e46ed4131c1b755ecfd2f6ed5d9675f","tid":558053,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"壓力大同夠唔夠訓都好大影響<br />\n我唔係食好多菜同生果，但只要夠訓第二朝一定好暢順"},{"pid":"69ff798912990510806594076a7d45c9e83c29ef","tid":558053,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"有冇食過勁污jo既野搞到自己肚屙有屎出？"},{"pid":"1d7234b53c41c464cea93512a323d52e51012467","tid":558053,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69ff798912990510806594076a7d45c9e83c29ef","tid":558053,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"有冇食過勁污jo既野搞到自己肚屙有屎出？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"我肚屙嗰陣都係會便秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c6bda3a181c4bed4c9037db76792670c2d7cf6","tid":558053,"uid":19285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"試下中藥食巴豆"},{"pid":"6b2397d41c51532644e05b69085b1602c7c1cebc","tid":558053,"uid":166568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"相反喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一離開香港就完全大唔出<br />\n試過去台灣8日同日本6日都冇大便<br />\n勁辛苦 個肚唔漲到一個點 日日有入冇出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b97c965d7bdc2b666b7eb2d5bee7d2372212d9","tid":558053,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b2397d41c51532644e05b69085b1602c7c1cebc","tid":558053,"uid":166568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"相反喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一離開香港就完全大唔出<br />\n試過去台灣8日同日本6日都冇大便<br />\n勁辛苦 個肚唔漲到一個點 日日有入冇出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"Google咗旅行便秘好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}